'''铃兰属'''（[[学名|学名]]：''Convallaria''）为[[天门冬科|天门冬科]]的一个[[属|属]]。

==物种==
本属包括以下物种：
* ''Convallaria aetnea'' Tornab.
* ''Convallaria doorata'' Mill.
* ''Convallaria glabra'' Kit.
* ''Convallaria globosa'' Greene
* [[小芦铃|小芦铃]] ''Convallaria keiskei'' Miq.<ref>Araki K ,  Shimatani K ,  Ohara M . Floral distribution, clonal structure, and their effects on pollination success in a self-incompatible Convallaria keiskei population in northern Japan[J]. Plant Ecology, 2007, 189(2):175-186.</ref>
* ''Convallaria latifolia'' Lam. ex Steud., 1840
* ''Convallaria latifolia'' Savi
* ''Convallaria laxiflora'' (Hemsl.) Druce, 1914
* [[欧铃兰|欧铃兰]] ''Convallaria majalis'' L.
* ''Convallaria nervulosa Druce, 1914
* ''Convallaria polygonatum'' Muhl.
* ''Convallaria polygonatum'' Thunb., 1784
* [[铃兰|铃兰]] ''Convallaria pseudomajalis'' W.Bartram
* ''Convallaria salvini'' Druce
* ''Convallaria sessilifolia'' (Baker) Druce, 1914
* ''Convallaria sibirica'' Schult.f., 1829
* ''Convallaria thyrsoidea'' (Hemsl.) Druce, 1914

